[normal]the one that is getting 
[normal]£
[normal]1,800 is better off.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Q17 [bold]&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Chris Williamson:[bold] We constantly get into this battle, 
[normal]though, 
[normal]do
[normal]n’t
[normal] we
[normal], between this definition of spending power and grant settlements?  There is a 
[normal]constan
[normal]t
[normal] tension, it seems, between DCLG’s interpretation of
[normal] what the figures are saying and your arguing, “These 
